channel.title: Does anyone have an open-sourse client with 471 gameframe? (Silab preferred)
channel.description:
I have downloaded like 7 clients, all saying the have 471 game frame but they don't... I'm tired of going through 100's of pages just to find a client that claims to have the new game frame.
Does anyone have an open-source client with 471 game frame, (silab items preferred)?
If you have a server to go along with it, I'd really appreciate that too :)
